# Netlify Redirects Configuration for Rosehill Energy
# Redirects from rosehill.energy AND rosehilloffshore.com to energy.rosehill.group

# Force old domains to new subdomain - rosehill.energy
https://rosehill.energy/* https://energy.rosehill.group/:splat 301!
http://rosehill.energy/* https://energy.rosehill.group/:splat 301!
https://www.rosehill.energy/* https://energy.rosehill.group/:splat 301!
http://www.rosehill.energy/* https://energy.rosehill.group/:splat 301!

# Force old domains to new subdomain - rosehilloffshore.com
https://rosehilloffshore.com/* https://energy.rosehill.group/:splat 301!
http://rosehilloffshore.com/* https://energy.rosehill.group/:splat 301!
https://www.rosehilloffshore.com/* https://energy.rosehill.group/:splat 301!
http://www.rosehilloffshore.com/* https://energy.rosehill.group/:splat 301!

# Force HTTPS
http://energy.rosehill.group/* https://energy.rosehill.group/:splat 301!
http://rosehillenergy.netlify.app/* https://rosehillenergy.netlify.app/:splat 301!

# Clean URLs - remove .html extension (redirect .html to clean)
